OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy day with outbreaks of
OL,6,Frain, this turning heavy at times. A
OL,7,Ffew limited brighter intervals in east
OL,8,Flater, where it could be quite warm.
OL,9,FMore showery in evening.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA cloudy evening and night
OL,12,Fwith spells of showery rain. Rain will
OL,13,Fbe locally heavy at times at first,
OL,14,Fbut becoming somewhat drier for a
OL,15,Fperiod after midnight.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FPartly cloudy with showers
OL,18,Fdeveloping, some heavy and merging
OL,19,Finto longer spells of rain, with a
OL,20,Frisk of thunder.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
